          totalDespesas
        )}</strong></span></div><div style="display:flex; justify-content:space-between; padding:0.5rem 0 0.5rem 2rem;"><span>Despesas Fixas</span><span>${fmtValor(
          despesasFixas
        )}</span></div><div style="display:flex; justify-content:space-between; padding:0.5rem 0 0.5rem 2rem;"><span>Despesas Variáveis</span><span>${fmtValor(
          despesasVariaveis
